Create the database module. Reference REARCHITECTURE.md ┬¦4 "Database Setup" and "Schema."

`engine/store/db.ts`:
- `openDatabase(dbPath: string): Database.Database` -- opens SQLite with WAL, NORMAL sync, 5s busy timeout, foreign keys ON
